KEY TO ABBREVIATIONS AND LETTER GRADES
MTM = Midterm Mark; ETM = End of Term Mark; TEM = Term Exam Mark; AVG = Class Average;
90 – 100 = A; 80 – 89 = B; 70 – 79 = C; 60 – 69 = D; 50 – 59 = E; 00 – 49 = F;
DIRECTOR OF STUDIES, PAULIN NDAHAYO
